Type Description <code>ErrorInvalidAddress</code> If any filter address is invalid <code>ErrorUnsupportedChainID</code> If the chain ID is not supported Example <pre><code>import { ChainId, EscrowStatus } from '@human-protocol/sdk';

const filters = {
  status: EscrowStatus.Pending,
  from: new Date(2023, 4, 8),
