console.log('Found escrows:', escrows.length);
</code></pre>

Type Description <code>ErrorUnsupportedChainID</code> If the chain ID is not supported <code>ErrorInvalidAddress</code> If the escrow address is invalid Example <pre><code>import { ChainId } from '@human-protocol/sdk';

