Type Description <code>ErrorProviderDoesNotExist</code> If the provider does not exist for the provided Signer <code>ErrorUnsupportedChainID</code> If the network's chainId is not supported Example <pre><code>import { KVStoreClient } from '@human-protocol/sdk';
